// Exponential search and Binary search , both codes are written below.
    // Revised Binary Search & Exponential Search

ğŸ” Analogy:
Imagine a library with infinite shelves. You want to find book #137. You:
Check shelf 1 â†’ not there
Jump to shelf 2 â†’ not there
Jump to 4 â†’ not there
Jump to 8 â†’ not there
Jump to 16 â†’ not there
